{"tid":1067832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"升降機失靈夾手不放　消防員撬門救出男子","createTime":"2019-03-18T21:59:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T23:09:42.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c841eaffb3c70975abf42aaf17173881d1596b20","tid":1067832,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T21:59:42.000Z","msg":"粉嶺欣盛苑欣彩閣，昨晚11時許，一名姓方26歲男子乘搭升降機返家時，發生驚險意外，遭升降機門夾住左手不能動彈，幸當時升降機並無移動，否則後果不堪設想，消防員趕至現場，撬開升降機救人，男子獲救後拒絕送院自行離開，發生故障的升降機事後關停進行檢查。"},{"pid":"e4a54463171b3b4a5c7c0752444fb7faba2de295","tid":1067832,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T21:59:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190319/59384266\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190319%2F59384266&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKhjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=4185debc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190319%2F59384266&h=772185d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190319/59384266</a>"},{"pid":"87d3a1562ab9d4fb46cec0a2ac58a6cca5844b3f","tid":1067832,"uid":55758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T22:01:06.000Z","msg":"緊係拒絕啦 咁撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce24ea09822daa888512d2ec5047edb105b50c3","tid":1067832,"uid":69924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T22:56:49.000Z","msg":"應該頂lift"},{"pid":"610bd314137088e0fd6d80f306468a12b85226c8","tid":1067832,"uid":99700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T23:08:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nx2rdCL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3